Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_cppr_o...le_factor_cell(25.10)    timing_cppr_o...le_factor_cell(25.10)

Name
       timing_cppr_opposite_edge_sigma_scale_factor_cell

Syntax
       timing_cppr_opposite_edge_sigma_scale_factor_cell <double >

       Default: 1

       Value Range: 0 to 1

       Controls  the  cell  sigma delay component for CPPR credit for opposite
       transition edges at the common pin.

       The scale factors are applicable only when  the  common  pin  has  mis-
       matched transitions for the launch and capture paths.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

